{
  "message": "test(fuzz): extend join_series corpus with 12 edge-case seeds\n\nAdd structured fuzz seeds covering:\n- Empty left/right series (inner_empty_left/right)\n- Duplicate labels (inner_dup_labels)\n- All-null values (outer_all_nulls)\n- Null value propagation (left_null_values)\n- Large label overlap (outer_large_overlap)\n- Disjoint labels (inner_no_overlap)\n- Asymmetric cardinalities (left/right_asymmetric)\n- Small cross product (cross_small)\n- Mixed dtypes (outer_mixed_dtypes)\n- Single element each (inner_single_each)\n\nTotal join_series coverage: 5 \u2192 17 seeds\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
